没了我对之前那些事儿记得也有点模糊了，我当时一时气的不行就把她给拉黑了。我也不太能找得到她了，我到底要不要再找她刺激刺激我啊，我感觉我情绪在被她弄崩一次，应该就能把剩下的写完了。或者披马甲找他，再让她虐我一回，我就能写出来了吧？小说卡在现在这部分卡的太难受了"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652623674"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiOCqj5qU7LQoEAMaCTEwNzMwNDk3MiCViN+wBjAAOCpACHIJNjUyNjIzNjc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1713017715.551969", "card_id": "Q_652646641", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《明日方舟》SideStory「巴别塔」剧情?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652646641"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiOCqj5qU7LQoEAMaCTEwNzMxMDA2MCD3puCwBjAAOCBACXIJNjUyNjQ2NjQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1713017715.553487", "card_id": "Q_652804842", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "35 岁后肿瘤发病率开始显著增加，普通人要如何应对？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据近期最新发布的全国癌症报告显示，35 岁以后癌症发病率开始显著增加，到 60 岁时发病率甚至是 30 岁时的 7 倍，而且每个人一生中罹患癌症的概率为 20% 左右，这对于许多人来说是一个不容忽视的问题。不过目前的医疗手段已相对先进，5 年生存率近 50%，带癌生存将越来越常态。对普通人来说，要如何应对这一新的形势呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac5fb665205d